      "text": "class MyDataClass(HyraxDataset)\n\ndef get_image(self, index):\n    # get .fits file by index\n\ndef get_a(self, index):\n    # get value from col a by index\n\ndef get_b(self, index):\n    # get value from col b by index\n\ndef get_c(self, index):\n    # get value from col c by index\n\ndef get_d(self, index):\n    # get value from col d by index",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "bIM6M25IL7bIoOT1rvKbf",
      "originalText": "class MyDataClass(HyraxDataset)\n\ndef get_image(self, index):\n    # get .fits file by index\n\ndef get_a(self, index):\n    # get value from col a by index\n\ndef get_b(self, index):\n    # get value from col b by index\n\ndef get_c(self, index):\n    # get value from col c by index\n\ndef get_d(self, index):\n    # get value from col d by index",
